task.summary: Restructured the test sources directory. Added Thesaurus class (not used yet) Changed the way object positioning works such that the first attempt to place an object is a better and more consistent guess.
Added distance interpreters. Improved pattern matching algorithm
Fixed dynamic programming approach to pattern matching sometimes not working, now passes all tests.
Fixed some smaller bugs in the pattern matcher, refactored it a bit. Restored some more patterns.
Added constantInterpreter Interpreter now uses proper KClass reflection, works with Int. Added group model interpretation. Added VariantModel
Kotlin-ized AbstractToConcrete modules. Started modifying AbstractToConcrete to move towards a side-effect-free style. Implemented simple size modifiers in concrete modeling.
Implemented relative position pst-resizing (not quite working right yet), cleaned up constraint code a lot. Fixed RelativePositionConstraint.a not being set.
Fixed relative positioning sometimes resulting in objects being inside one another.
Implemented relative constraints on group models. Refactored constraints. Other small changes.
Finally implemented cross-command component referencing. Refactored interpretation Introduced scaffolding types.
Finally implemented cross-command component referencing. Refactored interpretation Introduced scaffolding types.
Finally implemented cross-command component referencing. Refactored interpretation Introduced scaffolding types.
Kotlin-ized the primitive generator. Changed default size of sphere and cylinder to match the cube. Added support for prepositions on create commands themselves.
Refactored Model into derived/base. Created MutableRelativeSet Removed some unused classes. Introduced inline template interpret function.
